highlights.text: “לשוב הביתה” by Ishay Ribo has been on Top Songs Israel the longest, at 318 weeks straight.
“אני אוהב, אני מכור, אני שרוף” by Adir Getz is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Israel, up 85 spots at #113.
Omer Adam has the most spots on Top Songs Israel. “רק שלך” is the highest at #1.
“שיר לנטע” by ניר כנען is the highest new entry on Top Songs Israel at #125.
